rComments: Very Helpful and easy to talk to. Cares about students and about what he teaches. Knows his stuff and very passionate about it. Would recommend 100%

The man knows his stuff inside out. With Oxford University being his alma mater, the knowledge we were fed was significant! I loved going to class every time. Being in my third year, you would expect one would be jaded about lectures. Put in the effort and you'll get the A I got.
